Games::Risk
===========

The classical board game Risk written in perl.



INSTALLATION
============

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install



SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION
=========================

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc
command.

    perldoc Games::Risk

You can also look for information at:
  . Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Games-Risk
  . CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Games-Risk
  . AnnoCPAN, annotated CPAN documentation:
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Games-Risk
  . CPAN Ratings:
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Games-Risk



